Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Moscow's spy dust
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xl99
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 25 Aug 1985
Soviets admit to using chemical powder to trace movements and contacts of Americans living in Moscow. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less